code: @Bean public EhCacheCacheManager cacheManager(CacheManagerCustomizers customizers, CacheManager ehCacheCacheManager) {     return customizers.customize(new EhCacheCacheManager(ehCacheCacheManager)). }

@Bean @ConditionalOnMissingBean public CacheManager ehCacheCacheManager(CacheProperties cacheProperties) {     Resource location = cacheProperties.resolveConfigLocation(cacheProperties.getEhcache().getConfig()).     if (location != null) {         return EhCacheManagerUtils.buildCacheManager(location).     }     return EhCacheManagerUtils.buildCacheManager(). }
